 Sphink and chimera laughed. "Ok lets get this done" He put down the device 
and the ship appeared. "Now all scanning bots will think this is the ship. 
now that the ship has been moved to the moutain 10 miles from here. The other 
instrunment will keep it from being detected for a little while. now send the 
message informing everyone of this." The message went out in code only the 
council members could understand. it stated to go to these new coordinates 
where the ship had been moved. They where suggested to loose the bots.
